biz.paluch.logging.gelf.intern

Class GelfMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.paluch.logging.gelf.intern.GelfMessage

  • public class GelfMessage
extends Object
    Represents a Gelf message. A Gelf message contains all required Fields according to the Gelf Spec. A GelfMessage can be converted to toJson(), to toTCPBuffer() and to toUDPBuffers(). It also provides methods accepting ByteBuffer to reduce GC pressure.
    Author:
    https://github.com/t0xa/gelfj, Mark Paluch
    See Also:
    http://docs.graylog.org/en/2.0/pages/gelf.html
